# insights/

## What goes here
- One-off learnings worth remembering
- Single observations, realizations, or third-party lessons

## What does NOT go here
- Recurring observations with 3+ occurrences (→ `patterns/`)
- Actionable decisions (→ `decisions/`)

## Primary Home Test
File here if it's a single occurrence worth remembering.

## Naming Rule
`insight-name.md` (lowercase, hyphenated). Example: `llm-context-window-limits.md`

## Required Sections
- Executive Summary
- Bias Check
- Context (where/how learned)
- Compiled Truth
- Timeline Evidence
